name.en: Missing Burroughs, the Dark Ruler of the Highest Heaven
name.ja: <ruby>至<rt>し</rt></ruby><ruby>天<rt>てん</rt></ruby>の<ruby>魔<rt>ま</rt></ruby><ruby>王<rt>おう</rt></ruby>ミッシング・バロウズ

text.en: You can Special Summon this card (from your hand) by banishing 1 monster, 1 Spell, and 1 Trap from your GY. If this card is Special Summoned from the hand: You can banish 1 monster and 2 Spells/Traps from your opponent's field and/or GY. You can only use this effect of "Missing Burroughs, the Dark Ruler of the Highest Heaven" once per turn.
